 und Austarierens nähern kann. Der vorliegende Band widmet sich theoretischen wie künstlerischen Versuchen, Balancen zu denken und herzustellen.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aAby Warburg. 4aKultur. 4aÄsthetik. 7aART / General.2bisacsh1 aBlumentrath, Hendrik, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDe Vito, Emiliano, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDotzler, Bernhard J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEggers, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFischer, Ole W., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFriedrich, Lars, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFuchs, Margarete, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoebel, Eckart, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoebel, Eckart, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGormans, Andreas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrund, Simon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHauss, Philipp, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKerscher, Julia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMoog-Grünewald, Maria, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRathgeber, Pirkko, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSeidl, Ernst, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVehlken, Sebastian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aZumbusch, Cornelia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aZumbusch, Cornelia, eeditor.4edt